name: Your'e Not in The Room
description:
The memories sneak into my veins, knock me out cold. Are we dreaming this? don't wake me yet, it's dripping from your lips and written on your wrists; Can't be tamed.

You're not in the room, but you got me in a headlock, tied up, helpless, ready to be sacrificed and buried..

Love me.. Love me forever…
